{"id":253684,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-成都双流辛国惠北京上访回来被绑架/","date":"2012-09-25T16:01:09Z","modified":"2012-09-25T16:01:09Z","title":"维权网 | 成都双流辛国惠北京上访回来被绑架","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员陈华报道）成都市双流县东升白鹤社区<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>组的辛国惠于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点多钟，在距家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>米左右的地方，被七、八个不明身份的人，强行拖入一辆牌照为川</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">AN8Z57</span><span>的红色坨坨车内，疾驰而去。至今无任何消息。</span>  </p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1993</span><span>年，辛国惠家的土地和房屋被征用后，按照东升街道办的规定，在指定的地方修建了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">230</span><span>平米的商铺。一家人靠着做点小生意和出租铺面维持生活。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年初，东升街道办又以修建白鹤花园安置小区为由，再次要求征用。因这次拆迁的补偿过低，辛国惠没有签订拆迁安置协议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，东升街道办纠集当地公安、法院、工商等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>多人，没有出示任何手续，就对辛国惠家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">230</span><span>平米的铺面进行了强拆。但未得到任何赔偿。被强征的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">150</span><span>多亩土地，至今搁置荒芜，杂草丛生。几年来，辛国惠一家不断到双流县政府、成都市政府、四川省政府及公安、法院等地上访，均未得到任何处理。于是，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，辛国惠相约其他几个访民一起到北京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，辛国惠被成都市驻京办送回。当天，东升街道办派来的五个小伙子气汹汹的到火车站接辛国惠，其女儿见来者不善，打的将母亲接回。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点多钟，辛国惠被人绑架，不知去向，亦无任何消息。</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PW2e0eHEN14/UGHRg4q-S3I/AAAAAAAAPkM/30eG4w-yTjk/s1600/clip_image002.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PW2e0eHEN14/UGHRg4q-S3I/AAAAAAAAPkM/30eG4w-yTjk/s400/clip_image002.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5594948015587957068?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}